<section class="animal-page-section">


    <div class="description-half">

        <img class="zoosection-image" src="../Images/zoo-banner.png" />

        <p>
            Zoolirante will be home to a spectacular range of animals from across the globe, including awe-inspiring and endangered species. Stroll through the African Savannah to witness <strong>lions, giraffes, and cheetahs,</strong> wander the lively Primate Boulevard with <strong>gorillas and chimpanzees, </strong>and be captivated by the wildlife of South-East Asia, from <strong>tigers to elephants.</strong> Get closer than ever to Australia’s favourites in our open-range habitat, where kangaroos and wallabies hop freely along the pathways.

        </p>

        <p>
            Proudly Italian-owned and crafted with passion, Zoolirante blends global wildlife with <strong>European flair</strong> to create an unforgettable zoo experience.
